== 評價 ==
該系列的所有電影都在經濟上和批判性上取得成功，使該特許經營權成為類似於[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|占士·邦]]、[[星際大戰|星球大戰]]、[[夺宝奇兵|奪寶奇兵]]及[[加勒比海盗系列电影|魔盜王]]系列電影般的荷李活重要「支柱」之一。隨著每部電影的上映，觀眾們注意到該系列的視覺效果變得越來越[[黑暗奇幻|黑暗]]和越來越成熟<ref name="ColumbusDark"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://live.wsj.com/video/harry-potter-films-get-darker-and-darker/B5548BF1-3398-4597-9D4D-D5DD715DC6A3.html |title=Harry Potter Films Get Darker and Darker |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |date=2010-11-18 |access-date=2012-09-09 |archive-date=2012-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622184744/http://live.wsj.com/video/harry-potter-films-get-darker-and-darker/B5548BF1-3398-4597-9D4D-D5DD715DC6A3.html |url-status=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1910978,00.html |title=Harry Potter: Darker, Richer and All Grown Up |work=Time Magazine |date=2009-07-15 |access-date=2012-09-09 |archive-date=2012-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010145917/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0%2C9171%2C1910978%2C00.html |url-status=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-reviews-film-harrypotter-idUSTRE76609Z20110707 |title=Review: "Harry Potter" goes out with magical, and dark, bang |work=Reuters |date=2011-07-06 |access-date=2012-09-09 |archive-date=2013-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702034723/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/07/us-reviews-film-harrypotter-idUSTRE76609Z20110707 |url-status=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2011/12/03/isn%E2%80%99t-it-about-time-you-gave-the-chris-columbus-harry-potter-films-another-chance/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224124343/http://www.sfx.co.uk/2011/12/03/isn%E2%80%99t-it-about-time-you-gave-the-chris-columbus-harry-potter-films-another-chance/ |title=Isn't It About Time You Gave The Chris Columbus Harry Potter Films Another Chance? |work=SFX UK |date=2011-12-03 |access-date=2012-09-09 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，有些人對電影的看法普遍存在分歧，他們更喜歡首兩部電影較忠實的拍攝手法，而另一些人則更喜歡後期電影中更具風格化的角色驅動手法。

由於導演的轉變，以及由[[邁可·坎邦|米高·甘邦]]描繪的阿不思·鄧不利多一角跟理查德·哈里斯原本的描繪有所不同，有些人會認為這個系列有一種「不連貫」的感覺。作者[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]一直支持這些電影，並將《死神的聖物》評為該系列中她最喜歡的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.timeforkids.com/TFK/specials/potter/0,12405,184807,00.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070120181635/http://www.timeforkids.com/TFK/specials/potter/0,12405,184807,00.html |title=Potter Power! |work=[[Time_For_Kids|Time For Kids]] |access-date=2007-05-31 |archive-date=2007-01-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2004-05-27-potter-movie-book_x.htm |title=New ''Potter'' movie sneaks in spoilers for upcoming books |date=2004-05-27 |access-date=2007-05-31 |work=USA Today |last=Puig |first=Claudia |archive-date=2004-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040701142730/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2004-05-27-potter-movie-book_x.htm |url-status=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4410000/newsid_4415400/4415454.stm |title=JK "loves" Goblet Of Fire movie |date=2005-11-07 |access-date=2007-05-31 |publisher=[[CBBC|CBBC]] |archive-date=2007-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070317105424/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4410000/newsid_4415400/4415454.stm |url-status=no }}</ref>。她在其網站上寫到從小說到電影的轉變，「它需要把我的每一個故事情節都融入一部必須維持在四小時以內的電影中，這根本是不可能的事。顯然電影是有限制的—小說沒有時間和預算的限制；我可以單靠我自己與讀者想像力的互動來創造令人眼花繚亂的效果<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jkrowling.com/textonly/en/faq_view.cfm?id=94 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806214315/http://www.jkrowling.com/textonly/en/faq_view.cfm?id=94 |title=How did you feel about the POA filmmakers leaving the Marauder's Map's background out of the story? (A Mugglenet/Lexicon question) |publisher=J. K. Rowling Official Site |last=Rowling |first=J. K. |access-date=2007-10-08 |archive-date=2011-08-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。」

