== 榮譽 ==
在2011年2月舉行的《{{le|第64屆英國電影學院獎頒獎典禮|64th British Academy Film Awards}}》上，[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]、[[大衛·海曼|大衛·海曼]]、{{le|大衛·巴倫|David Barron (film producer)}}、[[大卫·叶茨|大衛·葉斯]]、[[艾方索·柯朗|艾方索·柯朗]]、[[迈克·纽维尔|米克·紐維爾]]、[[魯伯特·葛林|魯拔·格連特]]及[[艾玛·沃森|愛瑪·屈臣]]憑著該系列電影獲得「{{le|BAFTA英國傑出電影貢獻獎|BAFTA Outstanding British Contribution to Cinema Award}}」<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12353795|title=Harry Potter franchise to get Outstanding BAFTA award|publisher=BBC Online|date=2011-02-03|access-date=2011-02-03|archive-date=2012-07-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/694URQqSp?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12353795|url-status=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/outstanding-british-contribution-to-cinema-the-harry-potter-films,1631,BA.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110206001409/http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/outstanding-british-contribution-to-cinema-the-harry-potter-films,1631,BA.html|title=Outstanding British Contribution to Cinema in 2011 – The Harry Potter films|publisher=BAFTA|date=2011-02-03|access-date=2011-02-03|archive-date=2011-02-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

此外，[[美国电影学会|美國電影學會]]於2011年舉行的《{{le|美國電影學院獎|American Film Institute Awards}}》為整個系列授予一個特別獎。該特別獎是授予那些不符合AFI對其他在動態圖像方面擁有的傑出成就獲獎者的標準<ref name="afi.com">{{cite web|url=http://afi.com/afiawards/AFIAwards11.aspx|title=American Film Institute|website=afi.com|access-date=2013-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130913120743/http://www.afi.com/afiawards/AFIAwards11.aspx|archive-date=2013-09-13|url-status=yes}}</ref>。在其新聞稿中，該學院稱這些電影是「具有里程碑意義的系列電影；八部電影贏得了希望J·K·羅琳的心愛小說在銀幕上演活生命那一代人的信任。」隨著霍格華茲的魔法從電影中湧現出來，並深入到世界各地麻瓜的心靈和思想中，史詩般集體魔法的合奏賦予了我們跟哈利、榮恩和妙麗一起變老的禮物<ref name="afi.com"/>。」

《哈利波特》系列還獲得《{{le|BAFTA洛杉磯大不列顛獎|Britannia Awards}}》的認可，大衛·葉斯憑著其執導的四部《哈利波特》電影獲得「大不列顛藝術卓越獎」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://losangeles.broadwayworld.com/article/BAFTA-Honors-John-Lasseter-and-David-Yates-1130-20110628 |title=BAFTA Honors John Lasseter and David Yates 11/30 |publisher=Broadway World (Los Angeles) |date=2011-06-28 |access-date=2011-06-28 |quote=The worldwide success of Mr. Lasseter for Walt Disney and Pixar Animation Studios and Mr. Yates' contribution to the final four parts of the 'Harry Potter' franchise makes them global wizards in their own right, and are delighted to honor these remarkable filmmakers with this year's Britannia Award. |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107140250/http://losangeles.broadwayworld.com/article/BAFTA-Honors-John-Lasseter-and-David-Yates-1130-20110628 |url-status=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/awards/2011/06/john-lasseter-and-david-yates-set-to-be-honored-by-bafta-los-angeles-.html |title=John Lasseter and David Yates set to be honored by BAFTA Los Angeles |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-06-28 |access-date=2011-06-28 |archive-date=2011-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110703082314/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/awards/2011/06/john-lasseter-and-david-yates-set-to-be-honored-by-bafta-los-angeles-.html |url-status=no }}</ref>。

